CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 26, 1959, pg. A9 reads: "Christ In Christmas - As the Rev. J.A. Williams, pastor of the Baptist Temple Church, receives Miss Dorothy Meades as a new member of the church during Sunday morning worship, they symbolize the true spirit of the Advent Season, keeping Christ in Christmas. Miss Meades is a teacher in North Hills High School. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Reverend J.A.Williams, speaking to new member Dorothy Meades in Baptist Temple Church
